Going up against a large boss that (for some odd reason) doesn't have ungodly resists?<br>
<br>
Well, once MA has established sufficient aggro, unleash 3rd lvl of Host of Elements (9 elementals), wait about 40 seconds, then right click that dang epic of yours (20 second cast time) so that Epic appears when Mob-o-Elements poofs, send epic pet in, activate Servant of Ro, have it attack, buff Epic with BO4.....  Then nuke away. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
